headline: The Coca-Cola Company Announces Timing of Second Quarter 2025 Earnings Release
summary: ATLANTA, June 19, 2025--The Coca-Cola Company today announced it will release second quarter 2025 financial results July 22 before the New York Stock Exchange opens. The release will be followed by an investor conference call at 8:30 a.m. ET to discuss the results.
